{
  "stem": "6803.2",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And-- and there, I lived there for about 12-- for about nine months exactly.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And then after-- before there was about 10 or 12 days-- what have I figured out now was that 10 or 12 days-- was before the Americans came in-- they was liberating us-- they were still had this one [INAUDIBLE] that they had the only out of [INAUDIBLE] to [INAUDIBLE]-- to destroy the few poor little broken up Jews.",
      "word_count": 59
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So they made us stand up because in that Gusen Zwei, there was all nationalities-- Hungarians, Spanish, and-- and this and that.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I want to go back.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "In Gusen Zwei--",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "By the prisoners.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But there-- what I want to say is why, and even then they had that just one thing they had in mind, just to destroy the few people.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I want to go back now to, uh-- to what-- what-- what kind of a life we had in Gusen Zwei before we left Gusen Zwei.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "That is, I remember one time if you were sick, they put you in a hos-- so-called in a hospital, in a hospital.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I did not want to go there.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I just tried to be whatever I could to stay alive.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And one day-- I'll never forget that either.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And one day, there was-- they took all the people from the hospital.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "It was around January or February.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "It was bitter cold outside.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And they took all the people out of the hospital, and they just threw them out on the street, threw them out on the street, bare naked, in a-- in a bitter cold day.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In the camp.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "On the streets in the camp.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they were naked.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
